@Piet Fourie If they were trained by the Russians @Lex Luger OK - thanks for the heads-up. They should have refueled the plane at OR Tambo and sent it back to India.
Elton Bruce Thindwa,@Piet Fourie Dont abuse your freedom of speach .your Uncle was a water boy for the SADF @Piet Fourie Typical Coward personar @Pastor J Bona it makes my blood boil
Dominic Przybylski,Recently SANDF took part in a tank wargame competition in Russia. SANDF came last by a country mile. Everyone now knows that we are useless as a military force. In 1994 I celebrated because I believed we would all see each other outside of the prism of race. But race now has a higher profile in our communication than any other aspect of ourselves. Sad. We need a culture of individual responsibility """We do not have enough people who stand for what is right."" Summarizes the whole sorry mess." Chief of defence force would be cadre-deployment without a shadow of doubt. How could this man handle a real war if he was overwhelmed by a single incident in CAR and one helicopter crash? He rehearsed this 20 times infront of the mirror this morning. That's what it looks like to me. The buck doesn't stop in this country @Michael Wild Still haven't set up the checks and balances. How long does it take? The people at the top level of our country don't seem to be concerned enough to act upon anything except their own pensions. Interesting that our chief of the air force appears to be wearing a Chinese uniform. DIRCO is organisation for international relations and the sergeant-major... major cannot testify in English but was promoted to that organisation??? This man speaks like a dishonest politician. He doesn't speak like a military commander. Should never happen again - What does the promotion of the individuals involved say about it. It is SUPPOSED to be there to defend us. The people with integrity were kicked out and the people who were corrupt were promoted. That's what I got out of this testimony.
